Vetkoek: 4 cups flour ½ cup sugar ½ sachet instant yeast 1 tbsp oil ½ tbsp salt 1 ½ cups water, lukewarm 3 cups vegetable oil, for deep frying Caramel filling: 1 can Nestlé Caramel Treat 1 cup cream Topping: 2 cups milk chocolate, broken into small pieces 1 cup cream 1 cup Nestlé Peppermint Crisp chocolate, crumbled